## Instructions
Analyze lateral movement patterns:
1. Query authentication logs for the focus host/user
2. Identify connections to/from other hosts
3. Look for admin tool usage (PsExec, WMI, WinRM, RDP, SMB)
4. Track credential usage across systems
5. Record lateral connections between hosts
6. Map the complete movement path
7. Call `lateral_complete` with scope and containment recommendations
